'''{{class|Actor}}'''

bool '''ActivateSpecial''' (bool ''death'' = false) {{git|f5bf1d0}}

==Usage==
Causes the caller to activate their attached [[special]] if any, according to its' [[activation]] flags and properties. Returns true if the actor was successfully activated.

===Parameters===
*''death'': Activated is meant to be death related (i.e something that activates when the actor dies/is destroyed).

